{"tid":536231,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"一人一個意見對今年恒指既睇法！","createTime":"2018-01-21T15:16:03.000Z","updateTime":"2018-01-22T15:02:06.000Z","uid":162303,"like":1,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"7193d1aa42f9f21f8652034cdb48666b29c54873","tid":536231,"uid":162303,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-21T15:16:03.000Z","msg":"財政預算案前見33000，各路英雄等睇政府再決定後市，因為之前林鄭施政報告都令各界滿意<br />\n所以之後呯呯聲上到宜家<br />\n<br />\n預算案後大約過埋年，開始陰跌，因為已經大約消化消息，4月前大約平穩，內地股應該唔太郁，因為中央政治局會執位，維穩住！<br />\n<br />\n好，4月後內地各人開始上位做野，做咩?例如出招打擊走資，內銀監管等，內地穩定樓市等！<br />\n內銀內房內險開始有危險！<br />\n咁成個股市大約開始陰跌！"},{"pid":"efe21584cc636e6dad9f813a7ba8861aec5add5f","tid":536231,"uid":745,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-21T15:26:39.000Z","msg":"On撚尻<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"105d91d156102567077c6a37ea650ad50a13d6b4","tid":536231,"uid":99433,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-21T19:27:07.000Z","msg":"LM"},{"pid":"3df22e48b11d98ebc58321eb1d8f5a790910a4ba","tid":536231,"uid":109386,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-21T23:21:37.000Z","msg":"4萬點見"},{"pid":"9f4d4bdbdbfb7f4410e0b9f23062cd910d0d822f","tid":536231,"uid":104138,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-22T15:02:06.000Z","msg":"直上5萬典"}]}